<s> Wendy, I checked out the site, and read some of the titles.  </s>
<s> One of the articles disturbed me rather much.  </s>
<s> "Disabling Web Barriers" had a subtitle that said "incresing use of dynamic content, multimedia advances could foil disabled users ability to surf the net."  </s>
<s> In the article it said that the considerations for access to the web applied to both physically and cognitively impaired folks.  </s>
<s> No where in the article did it even suggest that multi-media advances would enable surfing by increasing numbers of cognitively-disabled folks, but instead implied that progress would impede use by "the disabled".  </s>
